Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe soul of a believer remains suspended by his debt until it is paid.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 1078 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2675,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/03\/31\/good-character-heaviest-mizan\/","url_meta":{"origin":42092,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Good character is heaviest on the Scale","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 31, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Darda reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNothing is heavier upon the scale of a believer on the Day of Resurrection than his good character. Verily, Allah hates the vulgar and obscene.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2002 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Tirmidhi \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0627\u0644\u062f\u064e\u0651\u0631\u0652\u062f\u064e\u0627\u0621\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0651\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38808,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/16\/wailing-makruh\/","url_meta":{"origin":42092,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Funerals: Angels prod those who wail over his grave","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 16, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Musa al-Ash\u2019ari reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo person dies and people stand over him wailing, saying, \u2018What a great man he was! How dignified he was!\u2019 but that two angels are appointed over him to prod him, saying, \u2018Is that really\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12997,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/20\/believer-learning-khayr\/","url_meta":{"origin":42092,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Knowledge: Believers never stop learning good","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 20, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe believer is never satisfied from learning good until he arrives in Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2686 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u062f\u064d \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064f\u062f\u0652\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":2737,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/01\/wisdom-lost-property-believer\/","url_meta":{"origin":42092,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Hikmah: Wisdom is the lost property of believers","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 1, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe word of wisdom is the lost property of the believer. Wherever he finds it, he is most worthy of it.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2687 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":21095,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/25\/mawt-fear-hope-salvation\/","url_meta":{"origin":42092,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Death: Fear and hope at the time of death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 25, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, entered the home of a young man in the throes of death. The Prophet said, \u201cHow do you feel?\u201d The man said, \u201cBy Allah, O Messenger of Allah, I hope in Allah and I fear for my sins.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627